\t<span>キャリア</span>\n\t\t<span>カムバック採用</span>\n\t</h2>\n</header>\n\n<header class=\"header\">\t\n\t<div id=\"header_nav_area\"><!--  #header_nav_area -->\n\t\t<nav>\n\t\t<div class=\"header_nav_area_inner\">\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"nav_list\">\n            <li><a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/about/\">ABOUT US</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/message/\">MESSAGE</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/interview/person1/\">INTERVIEW</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/requirements/\">募集要項</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/qa/\">Q&A</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/\" target=\"_blank\">コーポレートサイト</a></li>\n\t\t\t<li><a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"btn_close\">\n\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t</nav>\n\n\t\t<div class=\"btn_open\">\n\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t<span></span>\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\n\t\t<div class=\"toggle_btn_bg\"></div>\n\n\t  <div id=\"mask\"></div>\n\n\t</div><!--  END #header_nav_area -->\t\n</header><body class=\"home blog wp-theme-shikokuiryoki_recruit\">\n\n<main>\n\n    <div class=\"mv\">\n        <h1 class=\"mv_txt\">\n            <img src=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/wp-content/themes/shikokuiryoki_recruit/images/top/mv_copy.svg\" alt=\"今と未来の医療を支え健康を守る人を。\">\n        </h1>    \n\n        <ul id=\"slider_wrap\">\n            <li class=\"slide_item\">\n                <img class=\"toggleImg\" src=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/wp-content/themes/shikokuiryoki_recruit/images/top/mv_1_pc.png\" alt=\"四国医療器 リクルートサイト\">\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"slide_item\">\n                <img class=\"toggleImg\" src=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/wp-content/themes/shikokuiryoki_recruit/images/top/mv_2_pc.png\" alt=\"四国医療器 リクルートサイト\">\n            </li>        \n        </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <section class=\"sec sec_about\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <h2 class=\"ttl effect_fade\">\n                <img src=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/wp-content/themes/shikokuiryoki_recruit/images/top/about_copy.svg\" alt=\"私たちが想う医療機器販売という仕事。\">\n            </h2>\n            <h3 class=\"copy\">\n                <span>医療・理化学分野において</span><span>顧客が必要とする価値とは</span><span>適切なタイミングで必要に応じた</span><span>医療機器製品をご提案・お届けすること。</span>\n                <span>モノや情報をタイムリーにご提供し、医療・理化学に携わる人々に貢献することが</span><span>わたしたちが創造する付加価値の原点です。</span>\n                <span>これからも、社是「誠実」のもと地域社会に信頼される企業としてあり続けます。</span>\n            </h3>\n            <a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/about/\">ABOUT US</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"sec sec_message\">\n        <a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/message/\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <h2 class=\"ttl effect_fade\">MESSAGE</h2>\n            <h3 class=\"hl effect_fade\">私たちが伝えたいこと</h3>\n\n            <span class=\"btn effect_fade\">READ MORE</span>\n            </div>\n        </a>\n        \n\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"sec sec_connect effect_fade\">\n        <div class=\"txt\">\n            <div class=\"connect\">CONNECT</div>\n            <p>医療現場と医療機器メーカーとの<br>間をつなぐ、つなげる。</p>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n            <span></span>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n\n    <section class=\"sec sec_interview\">\n        <div class=\"inner\">\n            <div class=\"ttl_wrap\">\n                <h2 class=\"ttl\">INTERVIEW</h2>\n                <div class=\"hl\">先輩インタビュー</div>\n                <a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/interview/person1/\">READ MORE</a>\n            </div>\n\n            \n<div class=\"interview_slide\">\n\t<div class=\"slick clearfix\">\n\t\t<a href=\"https://shikokuiryoki.com/recruit/interview/person1/\"><img class=\"toggl